Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.93,0:00:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 吶 小鳩 小鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 給我唸唸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢火蟲之光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(螢火蟲之光 作 森颯太郎 畫 新村奈緒子)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.81,0:00:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 唸唸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳩難不成不會念吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.62,0:00:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會念的啦

Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:44.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}どうすうればいいんだっけ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.82,0:00:44.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}該怎麼辦才好來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.88,0:00:49.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fad(300,300)}あたりまえのことっていつも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.88,0:00:49.11,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}{\fad(300,300)}理所當然的事情總是這麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.01,0:00:52.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}難しいな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.01,0:00:52.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}紛繁複雜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:55.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}嬉しいとき笑って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.35,0:00:55.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}只是想開心的時候就笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:01:00.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}好きなときに歌いたいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:01:00.56,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}想唱歌的時候就唱歌而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:03.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:03.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:09.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}いつか願いは叶うと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.52,0:01:09.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}常說願望總會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:16.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}でもいつかってどれくらい待ちきれないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.67,0:01:16.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}可是總會到底要多久　已經等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:19.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}１ ２ ３　の合図で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:19.26,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}看好1 2 3的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:22.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}両手　ひろげて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.58,0:01:22.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}張開雙臂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.45,0:01:27.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}全身に　光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.45,0:01:27.37,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让全身充满光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:29.99,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}どこに　あるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:29.99,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}告訴我在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:33.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}教えて私にできること
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:33.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:36.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}目一杯　傷ついて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.79,0:01:36.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}傷得滿目瘡痍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.63,0:01:39.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}精一杯　走って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.63,0:01:39.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}跑的精疲力盡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:43.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}何十回　転んで泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.43,0:01:43.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}幾十次摔倒哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:46.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}それでもまた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:46.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}即使是這樣還
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:50.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}あきれるくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:50.21,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}難以置信地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:54.67,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}明日を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:54.67,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}相信著明天

